# Cricket Match Prediction API

A FastAPI-based cricket prediction system for T20 World Cup matches.

## Features

- Match winner prediction
- Playing 11 selection
- Score prediction across different innings phases

## API Endpoints

- `GET /` - Health check
- `POST /predict_match` - Predict match winner
- `POST /predict_playing11` - Predict optimal playing 11
- `POST /predict_score` - Predict scores and wickets

## Usage

The API accepts JSON requests with cricket match features and returns predictions.